trans-unit.source: An inline-level flow content element that provides facilities for hosting hyperlinks within flow content.
trans-unit.target: Um elemento de conteúdo de fluxo de nível de inline que fornece instalações para alojar as hiperligações no conteúdo do fluxo.

trans-unit.source: Hyperlink implements the <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink.NavigateUri%2A> property that you set with the <xref:System.Uri> of the content that should be navigated to when the Hyperlink is clicked.
trans-unit.target: HYPERLINK implementa o <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink.NavigateUri%2A>propriedade definida com o <xref:System.Uri>do conteúdo que deve ser utilizado quando se clica na hiperligação.</xref:System.Uri> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink.NavigateUri%2A>

trans-unit.source: Hyperlink navigation can only occur, however, if either the direct or indirect parent of a Hyperlink is a navigation host, including <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>, or any browser that can host [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xbapsharpplural-md.md)] (which includes [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie7-md.md)], [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie6](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie6-md.md)], and Firefox 2.0+).
trans-unit.target: Navegação hyperlink só pode ocorrer, no entanto, se direta ou indireta principal de um Hyperlink for um anfitrião de navegação, incluindo <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>, ou qualquer browser que pode alojar [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xbapsharpplural-md.md)] (que inclui [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie7-md.md)], [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie6](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie6-md.md)]e o Firefox 2.0 +).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see the **Navigation Hosts** topic in [Navigation Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações, consulte o **navegação anfitriões** tópico [descrição geral de navegação](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Hyperlink enforces a strong content model for child content.
trans-unit.target: HYPERLINK impõe um modelo de conteúdo seguro para o conteúdo subordinado.

trans-unit.source: See [TextElement Content Model Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) for more information about the Hyperlink content model.
trans-unit.target: Consulte [descrição geral do modelo de conteúdo TextElement](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) para obter mais informações sobre o modelo de conteúdo da hiperligação.

trans-unit.source: > [!IMPORTANT] > Depending on the host computer's security configuration, certain forms of navigation (for example, navigating to a [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_unc](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-unc-md.md)] path) are not allowed in the Internet zone.
